 consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"title":"MLNMultiPolygon","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"abstract":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON"},{"type":"text","text":" code. A shape source is added to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can update a shape source by setting its "},{"code":"shape","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"URL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeSource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource"}}}